WEBVTT

00:00:11.240 --> 00:00:14.326 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In Nehemiah’s day, the Jews joyfully embarked

00:00:14.326 --> 00:00:16.787 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
on a massive building project.

00:00:16.787 --> 00:00:18.789 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
With Jehovah’s direction and help,

00:00:18.789 --> 00:00:20.457 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
they were able to finish the work

00:00:20.457 --> 00:00:22.710 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
in just 52 days.

00:00:22.710 --> 00:00:25.004 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You look like you’ve been working.

00:00:25.004 --> 00:00:27.464 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
During the production of the film

00:00:27.464 --> 00:00:30.968 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
<i>Nehemiah:</i>
<i>“The Joy of Jehovah Is Your Stronghold,”</i>

00:00:30.968 --> 00:00:34.054 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the walls of Jerusalem were built once again,

00:00:34.054 --> 00:00:38.392 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
but this time at the Mount Ebo studios
in Brewster, New York.

00:00:41.437 --> 00:00:44.648 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
A variety of skills were needed
to produce this drama

00:00:46.525 --> 00:00:49.111 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
with many volunteers coming together,

00:00:49.111 --> 00:00:52.072 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
using their time, energy, and abilities

00:00:52.072 --> 00:00:55.159 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to create an accurate teaching tool.

00:00:55.993 --> 00:00:58.704 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And they found great joy in their work.

00:01:15.137 --> 00:01:18.557 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Good planning was needed
right at the start of production.

00:01:21.602 --> 00:01:24.563 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Every day began with a Scriptural discussion

00:01:24.563 --> 00:01:26.315 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and prayer.

00:01:29.276 --> 00:01:31.362 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The costume and makeup departments

00:01:31.362 --> 00:01:33.781 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
prepared the actors to appear on set.

00:01:41.121 --> 00:01:43.624 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Assistance was provided to help actors

00:01:43.624 --> 00:01:46.710 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
feel more comfortable
in front of the cameras.

00:01:50.422 --> 00:01:52.257 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And action!

00:01:54.385 --> 00:01:56.553 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Brothers, please.

00:01:56.553 --> 00:01:58.389 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Have they attacked anyone yet?

00:01:58.389 --> 00:01:59.306 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
They must have.

00:01:59.974 --> 00:02:01.809 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
No! But they will.

00:02:01.809 --> 00:02:05.020 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
While the production team
was filming in one studio,

00:02:05.020 --> 00:02:08.107 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
sets were being prepared in another.

00:02:11.318 --> 00:02:14.780 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
To add to the realism,
detailed props were made

00:02:14.780 --> 00:02:17.282 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
—many using 3D printing.

00:02:21.662 --> 00:02:24.999 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
With all of these researched
and crafted costumes,

00:02:24.999 --> 00:02:27.501 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
sets, and props combined,

00:02:27.501 --> 00:02:31.755 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
environments were designed
to accurately recreate the time period.

00:02:35.718 --> 00:02:38.721 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But even more was needed
to convey what it was like

00:02:38.721 --> 00:02:41.682 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to live in Jerusalem during Nehemiah’s day.

00:02:41.682 --> 00:02:45.269 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
For example, there were many animals on set.

00:03:11.545 --> 00:03:15.090 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Even after principal filming was completed,

00:03:15.090 --> 00:03:17.051 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
sets built in the studio were extended

00:03:17.051 --> 00:03:20.345 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
using advanced visual effects.

00:03:21.722 --> 00:03:24.433 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Digital construction work was done

00:03:24.433 --> 00:03:26.518 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
by the visual effects team.

00:04:06.058 --> 00:04:10.312 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Yes, building is a legacy of God’s people.

00:04:13.816 --> 00:04:16.276 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Nehemiah was one of many
who throughout history

00:04:16.276 --> 00:04:20.239 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
devoted their energies
to supporting the work of building.

00:04:22.950 --> 00:04:25.744 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In a similar way,
the production team that made

00:04:25.744 --> 00:04:29.498 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
<i>Nehemiah:</i>
<i>“The Joy of Jehovah Is Your Stronghold,”</i>

00:04:29.498 --> 00:04:32.084 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
joyfully worked hard to produce a film

00:04:32.084 --> 00:04:35.546 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that helps build love and appreciation

00:04:35.546 --> 00:04:37.589 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
in the hearts of God’s people.

